{"tid":726700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"菲律賓總統杜特爾特：上帝都戇鳩","createTime":"2018-07-02T15:29:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T00:45:55.000Z","uid":76115,"like":316,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"abe8b40145b1ed3706ea6697eb3a5fe15e917a63","tid":726700,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T15:29:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180627/bknint-20180627021438255-0627_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180627%2Fbknint-20180627021438255-0627_17011_001.html&d=wYJ3saCtSGZJu1oBX3652UkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=0ec03b0d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180627/bknint-20180627021438255-0627_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n菲律賓總統杜特爾特向來口無遮攔，他上周五（22日）演講時公開責罵天主「愚蠢」。由於該國有80%人口信奉天主教，有關言論引來國民嘩然；天主教會領袖紛紛作出譴責，其中一名主教更稱：「他不尊重天主教信仰，怎麼能夠作為菲律賓人的總統？」<br />\n<br />\n杜特爾特當日以《聖經》創世紀的故事，質疑天主為何創造了亞當和夏娃，又讓他們面對引誘，因而產生原罪：「這個愚蠢的天主是誰？你創造了完美，然後製造事端來引誘、毀掉自己作品的品質。」<br />\n<br />\n天主教主教大衞（Pablo Virgilio David）在Facebook發文，質疑一個不尊重天主教的人，不能成為所有菲律賓人的總統；菲律賓福音派教會委員會加入批評行列，斥杜特爾特「咒罵大多數菲律賓人虔誠信仰的天主和基督信仰」。<br />\n<br />\n杜特爾特周一仍就言論「死撐」；惟總統府發言人周二表示，杜特爾特已成立一個3人委員會，就他的發言與宗教團體對話。杜特爾特的鐵腕掃毒戰爭，造成數千人遇害，引來教會強烈批評，與天主教會關係勢成水火。"},{"pid":"7859ca7635fa52fdc2995cdf835d81c3d9d11051","tid":726700,"uid":30120,"like":247,"dislike":8,"score":239,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T15:30:48.000Z","msg":"佢話天主戇鳩又無講錯喎"},{"pid":"91b22a2970d9658463737c85c1baeae30bb04386","tid":726700,"uid":45213,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T15:35:28.000Z","msg":"3人委員會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64dc2a0e58390f6b3181800b44bb399b22920ecb","tid":726700,"uid":76115,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T15:37:59.000Z","msg":"&quot;Adam ate it (the fruit from the forbidden tree), then malice was born. Who is this stupid God? You are really a stupid son of a whore <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  if that is the case,&quot; <br />\n<br />\n&quot;You created something perfect, and then you think of an event that would tempt and destroy the quality of your work. How can you rationalise a God ... would you believe that?&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;What kind of religion is that? That's what I can't accept,&quot; <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2018/06/duterte-stupid-god-quip-personal-opinion-spokesman-180625082730103.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2018%2F06%2Fduterte-stupid-god-quip-personal-opinion-spokesman-180625082730103.html&d=wYJ3saCtSGZJu1oBX3652UkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=e8d19cdb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2018/06/duterte-stupid-god-quip-personal-opinion-spokesman-180625082730103.html</a>"},{"pid":"ccc611f3080d50d7aac681e11adc3ccea1bd93d0","tid":726700,"uid":76115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"91b22a2970d9658463737c85c1baeae30bb04386","tid":726700,"uid":45213,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T15:35:28.000Z","msg":"3人委員會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T15:38:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01614b8b25cfd1bcafa270d1422eae563dc28549","tid":726700,"uid":52595,"like":77,"dislike":3,"score":74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T15:57:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a4b790ab176dcc6143c11ca9d48636e5a7e4dcb","tid":726700,"uid":3936,"like":89,"dislike":1,"score":88,"quote":{"pid":"ccc611f3080d50d7aac681e11adc3ccea1bd93d0","tid":726700,"uid":76115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"91b22a2970d9658463737c85c1baeae30bb04386","tid":726700,"uid":45213,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T15:35:28.000Z","msg":"3人委員會<img src=\